8.11.18  12:30 am   man, i don't get it. i keep getting obsessed with the most random things, no matter how odd or out of the ordinary they are. it's like it's against my will. i end up being really embarrassed about some of my obsessions because they can make me feel "childish" or just weird in general (for example i was obsessed with a kids show for a while, i still like it but it was more embarrassing when it was my number 1 main obsession). i mean, if it were a harm to others, then yeah it'd probably be something i should worry about more but it's never really "harmful" to anyone. the closest i can think of to it being "harmful" is i feel really annoying sometimes when i talk about a specific thing a lot (i don't really know if i AM annoying or not but it really feels like i am to me but everyone always says i'm not so i don't really know what to believe anymore) but that's about it. i'm just confused. why do i do this???? is it really something i should be worried about i f it's not harming anybody??? i don't know. i just think about this a lot and i needed somewhere to Frickingggg put it so Here it is.
